{"tid":2251802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"母親節行街民安隊員涉藏打火機 被控意圖摧毀財産罪保釋候訊","createTime":"2020-10-21T05:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T05:13:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc244c56f6fc3defafd20fb04e9f83e9ddd799fb","tid":2251802,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"今年5月10日母親節，有網民發起「和你sing」及「母親節行街」，到全港多個商場唱反修例歌曲及叫口號。警方一度在旺角新世紀廣場使用胡椒球槍驅散聚集市民。其間一名民安隊員遭追截拘捕，搜出一罐打火機液體和兩個打火機，被控一項管有物品意圖摧毀財産罪，今在西九龍裁判法院提堂。裁判官應辯方要求，將案件押後至12月16日，以待索取法律意見後再作答辯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/J74DXU4UHFCNFIWPRPKVJOI7OI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FJ74DXU4UHFCNFIWPRPKVJOI7OI%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b61bb997\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FJ74DXU4UHFCNFIWPRPKVJOI7OI%2F&h=2c6b2fba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/J74DXU4UHFCNFIWPRPKVJOI7OI/</a>"},{"pid":"fcb21b8b838cd10ef5cd2664da01fa79857dafb5","tid":2251802,"uid":88879,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"食煙都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a35a28736550e13b1f6fe143de34affa923834","tid":2251802,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb21b8b838cd10ef5cd2664da01fa79857dafb5","tid":2251802,"uid":88879,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"食煙都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/